Mean lobster lengths in Isla Vista (mean ± sd [units], n = sample size) and Mohawk Reef (mean ± sd [units], n = sample size) differ signifcantly in 2012 and 2017 [t(630) = -1.88, p = 0.03, \(\alpha\) = 0.05], t(259) = 4.07, p = 0, \(\alpha\) = 0.05, respectively]). Notably, lobster length in 2017 was larger in 2017 than in 2012 for Isla Vista, an MPA site, and smaller for Mohawk Reef, a non-MPA site.
